From Backend Team

API

______

Get All Orders

GET request to /api/orders
Smaple Responses:
[
  {
    id: 1,
    name: 'James',
    drink: 'Coffee'
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    name: 'John',
    drink: 'Latte'
  }
]

______

Add an Order

POST request to /api/orders
Type: JSON

Smaple POST:
{
  name: 'John',
  drink: 'Coffee'
}

Sample Response:
{
  id: 3,
  name: 'John',
  drink: 'Coffee'
}

______

Update an Order

PUT request to /api/orders/{id}

Smaple PUT request:
PUT api/orders/1
{
  name: 'foo',
  drink: 'bar'
}

______

Delete an Order

DELETE request to /api